headline: How Investors Are Reacting To Verisk Analytics (VRSK) Partnering With Earnix To Automate Insurance Compliance
summary: On November 12, 2025, Earnix announced a new integration with Verisk Analytics that enables insurance carriers to directly ingest Verisk's ISO Electronic Rating Content into Earnix’s Price-It platform, automating rating data and compliance processes for faster model deployment. This collaboration is engineered to help insurers accelerate regulatory filings, manage deviations with ease, and reduce manual rework, positioning Verisk as a key enabler of operational efficiency in the insurance...
